    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Containers or spaces maintained at a low temperature by means of ice or mechanical apparatus for the purpose of preserving its contents, especially food or drink.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
